## Mock Data Requirements

### Providers (10 total)

Create 10 realistic San Francisco-based home service providers across these categories: Plumbing, Cleaning, Electrical, Handyman, TV Mounting, Painting, Pest Control, Appliance Repair.

Each provider needs:
- Realistic business name (not "Provider 1")
- Owner/tech first name
- Star rating (range: 4.2–4.9)
- Review count (range: 28–340)
- Pricing structure (varies by provider — some flat rate, some hourly, some callout + parts)
- Service area within SF
- Distance from user (0.8 mi – 6.2 mi)
- 3-5 services offered with descriptions
- 3-5 time slots across next 5 days
- 3-5 customer reviews with names, dates, text
- Trust badges (Licensed, Insured, Background checked — not all providers have all three)
- Specialties / tags

### Primary user query

Default demo query: "I have a leaking kitchen faucet, need someone tomorrow morning, budget under $200"

Agent interpretation:
- Service: Plumbing — Leak repair
- When: Tomorrow morning (show actual date)
- Budget: Under $200
- Location: San Francisco (auto-detected)

Returns 5 matching plumbing providers from the 10, ranked by relevance.

### Bookings mock data

- 1 upcoming booking (confirmed, scheduled for 2 days out)
- 1 active booking (provider en route, arriving in 12 min)
- 2 past bookings (completed)

### Messages mock data

- 1 conversation with the active booking's provider (3-4 messages + system updates)
- 1 conversation with a past provider (short exchange)

